content: Click the Discord logo in the top left of the app. Otherwise, we can chat on here if this is easier. Don't post your phone number on here or in the messages, please! I can help on the platform only.
This will keep the messages under the thread so it doesn't clog up the chat for other new users, but all text is still visibile so others can benefit from the help.
Ok let me try again laptop discord
No problem! I would start by pulling up discord.com in your browser and clicking download. There is a web version, but the app is much better IMO
I get a discord image w an arrow towards applications folder
Nothing can be clicked on it is just an image
Is that when you click the download button?
Yes……There is upper right cue says open discord
Do you see these two buttons on the home page?
Okay it should have downloaded an .exe file or prompted you on where to save it. Navigate to your downloads folder and there should be a file there to open the installer
I'm using Win10 so yours might be a bit different
